<% content_for :title, 'About' %>

<div class="bg-gray-900 bg-center bg-contain rounded-xl md:rounded-none">
  <div class="flex flex-col max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5 py-10 text-center md:py-20">
    <h1 class="font-black font-header leading-none my-5 text-4xl text-white uppercase md:text-6xl">
      About
    </h1>
    <p class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl">
      We build &amp; buy small creative internet businesses
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="border-b border-t border-gray-200">
  <div class="align-middle md:flex items-center max-w-screen-xl mx-auto py-20 transform transition-all">
    <%= image_tag('blacksmith.gif',
      class: "block mx-auto h-60 w-60 md:h-96 md:w-96", alt: "Blacksmith working on his craft") %>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-black font-header my-3 text-gray-800 text-4xl md:text-6xl">
        Hard Work Montage
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-3 text-gray-500 text-xl md:text-2xl">
        <em>noun</em> [hahrd wurk mon-tah-zhiz]
      <p>
      <ul class="list-decimal mt-5">
        <li class="mb-5 ml-5 text-gray-900 text-xl md:text-2xl">
          A common TV and movie trope where one or more characters is shown working hard at a particular task through a sequence of shots meant to imply time passing.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-5 ml-5 text-gray-900 text-xl md:text-2xl">
          A holding company that builds and buys e-commerce, SaaS, content, community, and other internet businesses.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
  <div class="pt-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-black font-header text-gray-800 text-4xl uppercase md:text-6xl">
      <strong>People</strong>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto pb-5 pt-10 md:pb-20 md:px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse max-w-screen-xl mx-auto pb-10 py-5 md:flex-row md:pb-20 md:py-10">
      <div class="font-medium p-5 prose prose-lg md:p-10 md:pt-5 md:pl-0 md:prose-xl md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="font-black leading-none max-w-4xl my-2 text-2xl text-slate-900 md:mb-4 md:mt-2 md:text-5xl">
          Adam Howell
        </h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://adamhowell.org" target="_blank">Adam</a> is the founder and co-owner of Hard Work Montage.
        </p>
        <p>
          He is also a husband, dad, creator, and entrepreneuer living in Charlotte, NC.
        </p>
        <p>
          His work has appeared in 
          <a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2016/09/30/phoneys-ill-fated-tale" _target="blank">Daring Fireball</a>,
          <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2016/09/28/this-crazy-imessage-app-lets-you-prank-friends-by-putting-words-in-their-mouth/" _target="blank">TechCrunch</a>,
          <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/30/13127632/apple-demands-phoneys-imessage-sticker-app-changes" _target="blank">The Verge</a>,
          <a href="https://charlotte.axios.com/67868/adam-howell-local-technologist-hits-1-on-the-app-store-with-phoneys/" _target="blank">Axios Charlotte</a>,
          <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/06/technology/the-campaign-against-walmart.html" _target="blank">The New York Times</a>,
          <a href="https://www.newsweek.com/free-slackers-delight-117813" _target="blank">Newsweek</a>,
          and many more, plus he has appeared <a href="marketplace.mp3" _target="blank">as a guest on the NPR show Marketplace</a>.
        </p>
        <p>You can connect with Adam on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/badamhowell/">LinkedIn</a>, <%= link_to "contact him here", contacts_path %>, or email him at adam at hwm dot llc.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center md:w-1/3">
        <%= image_tag('img_mugshot.jpg', class: "rounded-full shadow-xl w-96 md:w-full") %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse max-w-screen-xl mx-auto pb-10 py-5 md:flex-row md:pb-20 md:py-10">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center md:w-1/3">
        <%= image_tag('img_stacey.jpg', class: "rounded-full shadow-xl w-96 md:w-full") %>
      </div>
      <div class="font-medium p-5 prose prose-lg md:p-10 md:pt-5 md:prose-xl md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="font-black leading-none max-w-4xl my-2 text-2xl text-slate-900 md:mb-4 md:mt-2 md:text-5xl">
          Stacey Howell
        </h2>
        <p>
          Stacey is a wife, mother, volunteer, and voracious reader living in Charlotte, NC.
        </p>
        <p>
          She also works alongside Adam as co-owner of Hard Work Montage.
        </p>
        <p>You can contact Stacey <%= link_to "here", contacts_path %>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
